@event change [Object]
  @description
    The event emit when the value of the single select is changed.

  @property cause [String]
    @description
      The cause of the event. Either @code[user] when caused by a user interaction
      or @code[api] when caused by calling the @code[value] method

  @property value [Any]
    @description
      The currently set value for the single select. Can be any of the @code[items]
      passed in, or @code[undefined]
